results.title: Live Love Laugh Charm Snap Bracelet, Love Live Laugh Charm Bracelet, Vegan Leather Snap Charm Bracelet, Ginger Snap Jewelry, Noosa Jewelry
results.description:
Brighten ♥ someone's day with this handmade cork leather bracelet with a live love laugh snap charm button. These charm bracelets are made with genuine cork imported directly from Portugal, home of the Cork Oak Tree. The cork for this bracelet is lightweight, durable, environmentally friendly, and a vegan option to leather.
  
My handmade cork bracelets are one-of-a-kind with a hand-riveted snap charm base in the center of the bracelet. This snap base enables you to switch out interchangeable 18mm snaps with whatever snap button you desire, making it a timeless jewelry piece. Change out your snap charm to go with your mood, holiday, season, or any occasion. If you get bored with the look of your bracelet, you can change it out "in a snap." These bracelets are made with a magnetic closure.

There are two cork options for this bracelet: natural or natural with silver sparkle. 

This cork bracelet measures:

♦ 1" width x 7.5” length with an 18mm hand-riveted snap base for interchangeable 18mm snap button charms (custom sizing on bracelet length available upon request)

Snap Jewelry Charm Care Instructions:

♦ These are fashion jewelry snap charms and can be made of various base metals such as Zinc Alloy, Copper, Silver, and/or Rhodium Plated. As with all fashion jewelry, tarnishing may naturally occur over time. If tarnishing does occur, use a dry polishing cloth to gently wipe them.

♦ Do not use jewelry cleaners or other chemicals, as these products are corrosive and will strip the finish on the snap charm jewelry causing permanent damage.

♦ Limit exposing your jewelry to water or sweating. Do not shower, swim, or work out with your jewelry. 

♦ When not wearing your snap charm jewelry, store in an airtight container or zip-lock bag.

What is Snap Charm Jewelry?

Snap Charm Jewelry is trendy and unique. Create your own one-of-a-kind pieces of jewelry "in a snap" with a variety of snap charm buttons. There are a variety of snap bases on the market to add your snap charms including earrings, bracelets, pendants, necklaces, brooch pins, etc. You won't get bored with your snap charm jewelry, just change out the snap button and voila!, you have a newly designed piece of jewelry. Change your snaps to fit your mood, holiday, occasion, or season.

WARNING:  CHOKING HAZARD - Small Parts - Fashion Jewelry - Not a Toy.

results.title: Live Laugh Love,Sublimation Transfer,  Mug Can Holder
results.description:
**Please note this is a sublimation transfer to be placed onto your shirt, creeper, mug, or can holder.

You must have  a heat press, because a  iron will not work. Transfer must be used on a shirt that is at least 50% polyester, but a 100% is preferable. A 50% polyester item will give you a  vintage look. Shirts should be light in color white or heather gray are best. The sublimation process involves the dye going into the item so if it is used on a dark colored shirt it will not show up well and if it is used on black will not show up at all.  


REQUIREMENTS:
-Heat Press (no iron)
-White or Light Colored Fabric (white and light heather grey are the best choices)
-Garment MUST be at least 50% polyester, the higher the poly content the more vibrant the colors (lower polyester content gives a vintage look).

Instructions: (detailed version shipped with order)

– medium pressure
